<br>
table
  tr
    th User
    th Last Logged In
    th Sign in Count

  tbody
    - customer = Customer.where(id: @customer_id).first
    - customer.projects.flat_map(&:users).uniq.each do |user|
      tr
        td= user.first_name
        td= user.last_sign_in_at
        td= user.sign_in_count